### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

###

### Test 1: Start Analysis (Real PR Example)
POST http://localhost:3000/analyze-pr
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "repo_url": "https://github.com/facebook/react",
  "pr_number": 28676
}

### Response will give you a task_id like: "abc-123-def-456"
### Use that task_id in the next requests!

###

### Test 2: Check Status (replace with your task_id)
GET http://localhost:3000/status/abc-123-def-456

###

### Test 3: Get Results (replace with your task_id)
GET http://localhost:3000/results/abc-123-def-456

###

### Test 4: With GitHub Token (for private repos or higher rate limits)
POST http://localhost:3000/analyze-pr
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "repo_url": "https://github.com/your-username/your-private-repo",
  "pr_number": 1,
  "github_token": "ghp_your_token_here"
}

###

### Test 5: Small PR for Quick Testing
POST http://localhost:3000/analyze-pr
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "repo_url": "https://github.com/vercel/next.js",
  "pr_number": 50000
}

###

### CURL Examples (copy-paste into terminal):

# Start analysis
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/analyze-pr \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"repo_url": "https://github.com/facebook/react", "pr_number": 28676}'

# Check status (replace task_id)
curl http://localhost:3000/status/YOUR_TASK_ID_HERE

# Get results (replace task_id)
curl http://localhost:3000/results/YOUR_TASK_ID_HERE